title: Good Omens Crack #1 (mostly Crowley & Aziraphale)
author: KatMoony
comment: i know he says “i lost my best friend” but it really sounds like “i loved my best friend” so uhhhh i cry

* Aziraphale exists *

Crowley: Oh shoot, now I'm gay.

I love how the whole GO fandom has collectively decided to protect Aziraphale like if he were a Cinnamon roll when he actually came up with the idea of murdering children and had a freaking flaming sword.
Every single video similar to this that I’ve watched has had Crowley on the “Move, I’m gay” vine.
I just realised how scottish David Tennent goes in the fire scene lol
